-- Rio Tinto says Australian rump sold at A$48.50
-- 
-- Fri Jul 3, 2009 4:26am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/07/03/uk-riotinto-rump-sb-idUSTRE5620TX20090703

 

 SYDNEY  (Reuters) - Underwriters to global miner Rio Tinto Ltd's ( RIO.AX ) ( RIO.L ) rights issue have sold the Australian "rump" at A$48.50 each, a 6.3 percent discount to Rio's last traded price, Rio said in a statement on Friday. 

 Australian shareholders had taken up 94.76 percent of their entitlements to the new shares under Rio's $15.2 billion rights offer. The remaining 7.87 million shares were sold to investors through a placement. (Reporting by  Denny Thomas )